text: Wildwood was a restaurant in Portland, Oregon, in the United States. It was founded by Cory Schreiber in 1994 and closed on February 25, 2014. ==See also== * List of defunct restaurants of the United States ==References== ==External links== * http://pdx.eater.com/2014/2/18/6277199/wildwood-will- close-next-week-after-20-year-run Category:1994 establishments in Oregon Category:2014 disestablishments in Oregon Category:Defunct restaurants in Portland, Oregon Category:Restaurants disestablished in 2014 Category:Restaurants established in 1994
title: Wildwood (restaurant)
